ed for the words “shall perform such duties and exercise such powers”. The words “of America”, “elements of”, “other provisions of”, and “so assigned” are omitted as surplusage.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idab61a5ae-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idab61a5af-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2019—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–92","children":[],"tail":" renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s9074"},"text":"section 9074 of this title","children":[],"tail":" as this section."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2018—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–232","children":[],"tail":" renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s8074"},"text":"section 8074 of this title","children":[],"tail":" as "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s9074"},"text":"section 9074 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2006—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/163"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–163","children":[],"tail":" struck out “its Territories,” after “the United States,”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2001—Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/107"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–107","children":[],"tail":" struck out subsec. (c) which read as follows: “The Military Air Transport Service is redesignated as the Military Airlift Command.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1986—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/433"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–433","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Except as otherwise prescribed by law or by the Secretary of Defense, the” for “The”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1965—Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/37"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–37","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (c)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1958—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/599/s4/f/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–599, § 4(f)(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted provisions permitting the Air Force to be divided into such organizations as the Secretary of the Air Force may prescribe for provisions which established an air-defense, a strategic, and a tactical command in the Air Force."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsecs. (b) to (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/599/s4/f/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–599, § 4(f)(2)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subsec. (d) as (b), and repealed former subsecs. (b) and (c) which permitted the Secretary of the Air Force to establish additional commands and organizations in the interest of efficiency and economy of operation, and, for the duration of any war or national emergency, to establish new major commands or to discontinue or consolidate major commands."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idab61a5b0-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idab61a5b1-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2018 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":